text: Hélène Receveaux (born 28 February 1991) is a French judoka.IJF profile She is the 2017 European bronze medalist in the 57 kg division ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:French female judoka Category:Living people Category:Universiade medalists in judo Category:Universiade bronze medalists for France
